Class ShippingSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • ShippingSection

  • public class ShippingSection
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Elliot Lohr This program provides a blueprint for a ShippingSection node, which will only take in orders that fit the bounds on the category of the order
